                    <h2>5 Apr 2009, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Film + Discussion. In homage to Douglas Sirk’s Hollywood melodrama, Fassbinder brings us the story of a young Moroccan mechanic who falls in love with a German widow almost 30 years his senior. Dr Tobias Hochscherf from Northumbria University will introduce and lead a discussion after this screening. 
